Address: 29/1 Greg Norman Drive Sanctuary Lakes VIC 3030
Description:
Supreme Sanctuary Lakes Location
As we are aware during this critical time and social distancing, it is now mandatory that you register for a private inspection and follow the government guidelines in this video https://youtu.be/2WCtGFNENYU
Positioned in the hot spot of Sanctuary Lakes, living on Greg Norman Drive is living at its finest.
If you are down-sizing, looking to invest or a first home buyer then this is the perfect opportunity for you. You will get all your boxes ticked for this beautifully presented home you've been waiting for.
The large driveway entrance with manicured lawn and landscape gardens will straightaway impress you as you walk in. Warmly greeted by cosy formal lounge room upon entrance with easy flowing floor plan to the open plan kitchen, living and dining including powder room.
Your kitchen features a generous size island bench which overlooks the main living/ dining and outdoor spaces. Complimented by stainless steel appliances including near new dishwasher with ample overhead cupboards and draws for all your kitchen storages.
Friends and family can spread out from the dining to the large outdoor entertaining area, fully paved and nurtured. Enough space for your gardens as well as great backyard entertainer's choice all year around. There's also a fully paved path surrounding the entire home for your convenience.
Stroll up the staircase to a central retreat area upstairs. The second level comes with three bedrooms all including their own balcony to enjoy. The master bedroom comes with walk-in robe and ensuite with double vanity. The other two bedrooms include built-in robes sharing a main central bathroom.
Adding further value to the home are features such as refrigerated cooling and heating, high ceilings, downlights throughout the house, ceiling fans in bedrooms and living areas. Fully landscaped front yard with double remote garage, built in shelves, large external storage space underneath the staircase for your convenient and back to base monitored alarm system.
Take a beautiful stroll around the forever famous lakes or walking along the creek and wetland reserve. This perfect location allows you to walk or a short drive to the Sanctuary Lakes Shopping Centre and local schools. Sanctuary Lakes Resort Estate offers 24 hours security patrol and a recreational club including gym and swimming pool.
Perfect home to start your property portfolio!

Description:
Dare to dream
If ever there was an opportunity to secure a brilliantly located home in a great neighbourhood, this would be it. Delivering huge appeal, this is an excellent chance to claim a potential-rich piece of real estate that lends itself to a host of options. Positioned on a block measuring 656sqm approximately, first homebuyers will relish the chance to buy their first property and refurbish to their own style, whilst investors will see the merit in buying a home in this sought-after locale. Keen renovators may like to add their own designer flair, whilst families looking to build their forever home or developers keen to start a new project (STCA) will also be impressed with what this classic home has to offer. Showcasing a traditional floorplan with a lounge and dining room, accompanied by a casual meals area and retro style kitchen. Three bedrooms are serviced by a central family bathroom. The location couldn't be better, a short walk from bus services, Talintyre Road Shops, many schools including St Peters Primary, Glengala Primary and Sunshine College West, Kororoit Creek trails including Buckingham Reserve plus only a short distance to Sunshine train station and Shopping district.

Description:
The Ultra Spacious Family Home !!!
Reliance Real Estate proudly presents this prime residence with in a highly sought after location in Tarneit. You feel the sheer luxuriousness, the moment you arrive at this ultra spacious family home built on a generous 512 sqm of land. With gorgeous low maintenance front yard to start with, then the stunning merbau decked front porch welcoming you inside. Stepping through inside, you are wowed by the stunning laminated floorboards running all through the lounge & kitchen area. At the centre of the home is the generous sized open plan living area alongside the dining area that just add that silver lining to stunning interiors of the house. The extra large separate theatre/rumpus room located at the rear end adds another dimension to this grand architecture.
Striking in appearance and functionality, the well-equipped & ultra spacious kitchen boasts of premium stainless steel appliances with dishwasher, stone bench top, 900mm cooking appliances, large sized walk-in pantry & ample storage which easily services the open plan dining and multiple living areas. Exquisite outdoor living with a fully decked verandah area overlooking lush green backyard, with an abundance of relaxation space, sitting area ideal for partying with family & friends.
This stunning home comprises of 4 generous sized bedrooms including large Master with its private ensuite & walk in robes whilst other bedrooms feature built in robes and serviced by large common bathroom.
In addition, this prestige family home features :
Dishwasher
High Doors
High Ceilings
Security Alarm
Ducted Heating
Mirror Wardrobes
Color bond fencing
Window furnishings
Evaporative Cooling
Dual Vanity in the ensuite
Wooden Plantation Shutters
Automated double garage with internal access

* Ultra-modern kitchen with stone bench tops, stainless-steel appliances, glass splash back & dishwasher
* Sparkling central bathroom
* Spacious separate front lounge room
* Ducted Heating, evap cooling, additional split system
* Downlights, high ceilings, square set cornices, polished concrete
* Alarm system, ducted vaccum...

* All set on a 654sqm ( approx ) allotment with large decked pergola & entertaining area, making it the perfect place for those large family gatherings.
* Situated in ' The Grove Estate ' all within close proximity to schools, sporting grounds, restaurants, Lake Caroline, West Waters Hotel, CS Town centre & generous parklands & walking tracks.
* Vibrant living designed for the lifestyle lover, Inspection is a must.

QUIET , LOVELY FAMILY HOUSE IN POINT COOK FOR SALE ( Private inspection Available ,please contact agent)
12 Tramway Street Point Cook
LJHooker City Residential presents 12 Tramway Street, Point Cook - a fantastic upsize for a growing family or equally a great investment in the property market!
This property offers 4 bedrooms, with the master bedroom consisting of WIR's and a sparkling en-suite. The second, third and fourth bedrooms include BIR's, along with a main bathroom placed conveniently between for easy access to all members of the household. An opportunity for a study or children's playroom could be an option if you felt like flipping a bedroom!
The kitchen has updated appliances and flows through to the dining and lounge area. Walking further leads you to the alfresco and backyard area, perfect to let children or pets play within! Tucked out of the way beside the kitchen is a complete laundry room, with access to the large double indoor garage. There is also room for excess parking outside the garage on the driveway.
Only a short drive from the main shopping centres, restaurants, public transport and schools, you'll be surrounded by everything you need! Please call Mia from LjHooker City Residential today on 0439 994 244 to book an inspection make an enquiry. Be quick as this delightful house won't last long!

Description:
Lot 2818 Eskdale Street PREMIUM - THE GROVE Collection 4
Build the home of your dreams in a natural wonderland at The Grove in the Riverwalk Premium precinct. In a prized location, neighbouring Carnboon Park, The Grove offers residents an unrivalled experience of parkside living. Create a family lifestyle to treasure with 4 parks nearby and over 10 hectares of parkland within five minutes of your doorstep. Be part of a welcoming community with a friendly village atmosphere and abundant opportunities for everyone to thrive.
An active healthy lifestyle is yours with four of Riverwalks parks within easy reach. Spend time at Carnboon Parks playground or share a BBQ with friends taking in the majestic heritage river red gums. Appreciate your neighbourhoods lush streetscapes with canopies of mature trees lining the manicured pathways.
Walk or cycle on the shared path that connects to the Federation Trail that accesses Werribees rich urban amenity. Step out to the neighbourhood bus stop where regular bus services will have you in the heart of Werribee and surrounding suburbs in no time at all.

Lot 2733 Newmarket Road PREMIUM - THE PROMENADE Collection 3
Create an enviable lifestyle at The Promenade, the gateway to the exceptional Riverwalk Premium within the established Riverwalk community in dynamic Werribee. Surround yourself with natural beauty in this exclusive parkside setting where more than 100,000 sqm of lush Riverfront parkland is just five minutes walk away.
The Promenades impressive entry features a wide tree-lined boulevard delivering a unique opportunity to nestle your dream home amongst mature trees and street landscaping. Enjoy an active lifestyle with the utmost convenience with Lollipop Creek and the Village Park within easy walking distance. A shared path will connect you to the Federation Trail that meanders beside the Werribee River for a scenic journey into the heart of Werribee. Take advantage of regular bus services to the suburbs flourishing amenity from a bus stop right on your doorstep. A premium parkside lifestyle by the river awaits at The Promenade.

Description:
PERFECT START FOR THE FIRST HOME BUYER
Located within a short distance to all local amenities Caroline Springs has on offer such as train station, CS Square Shopping Centre, quality primary and secondary schools and close to Taylors Hill Shopping Centre.
A delightful and surprisingly spacious family home sitting on a generous allotment in the ever popular Northgate Village Estate is a great opportunity for a first home buyer, down sizer or astute investor.
Comprising of three good-sized bedrooms to include large master bedroom with walk-in robe & ensuite, remaining bedrooms with built in robes and security shutters.
Modern kitchen features double gloss vinyl wrap kitchen with premium stone waterfall benches, glass splash-back, Bosch stainless steel appliances including 600mm hot plates, wall oven, range hood and dishwasher with adjoining meals and family area. Offering central bathroom, laundry, double remote garage with internal & external access leading to a double carport and pergola.
Added extras include gas ducted heating, refrigerated cooling, split system, LED down lights, 25 solar panels with 5 kw inverter, engineered floating floors in living zone, quality carpet in all bedrooms, garden shed, water tank. security cameras x5 and fully landscaped low maintenance gardens.
(Photo ID is Required at all Open For Inspections, Prior to Entry)

Description:
A beautifully renovated gem on 840sqm Land that too in the Cambridge estate!!!
The Reliable Duo, Pratik & Divyesh, of Reliance Real Estate proudly presents this ultra-spacious family home on a massive lot, of 840sqm (approx) land in Hoppers crossing's most sought after Cambridge Estate. You feel the sheer luxuriousness, the moment you arrive at this spacious family home. Stepping through the entrance, you are wowed by the original new timber looked tiled flooring running all through the lounge, living area & dining area.
This family-minded floor plan offers a luxurious spacious lounge & formal living area that is sure to leave an impression on all the guests. Facilitating a remarkable measure of natural light, this home offers 3 great sized bedrooms including Master with large built-in wardrobe, & its full ensuite with fully renovated new. Whilst the other bedrooms are fitted with built-in robes and are serviced by the central fully renovated new bathroom and separate laundry. The adjoining open plan living area followed by a dining area just adds that silver lining to the stunning interiors of the house.
Striking in appearance and functionality, well-equipped & ultra-spacious kitchen boasts of appliances with ultra-wide 40mm Laminex benchtop & ample storage which easily services the open plan dining areas.
The premium features do not stop there; You can truly feel the measure of adoration and care that has been put into keeping up the flawless state of the home as you venture outside; sliding entryways open onto your outside outdoors with bordering pergola & has got huge back entertaining area with the natural grass & has gone into ensuring that this exquisite lawn show is well adequate all through the majority of the seasons.
Just predict enjoying the great days of your life by facilitating family gets together during those soothing summer months with friends and family. Also, you will surely be impressed by the low maintenance front yards and has the double car garage plus dual side access points perfect for that boat, caravan or Trailer.
In addition, this prestige family home feature:
LED Downlights
Electric gas heater in the formal lounge
Ducted heating
Evaporative cooling
3 Living area
Quality window and security doors
All of the amenities are within close proximity:
Walking distance to Werribee Plaza Shopping Centre
- 450m (approx.) to Cambridge Primary school
-5 Min (Approx) to Hoppers Crossing train station
- 2-min walking distance to the bus stop (destination Hoppers crossing and Tarneit station).
- 6-mins (approx) to Aqua pulse
- 3mins drive (approx) to Hogan's Corner Reserve (Woolworths, Pharmacy, McDonald's and several fast-food restaurants)
With a beautifully presented home in a prime location, gorgeous backyard (the photos don't do it justice) and not to mention future development possibilities (STCA) on a corner block of 840m2 don't pass up on this amazing opportunity to secure one of the most versatile properties on the market today.
Grab this golden opportunity now and call Divyesh Waghela 0451 367 400 or Pratik Shah 0430 437 402 to arrange an inspection at your convenience before it's too late.

Convenience in The Grove!
Introducing an EAST facing block of land in The Grove Estate of Tarneit. This block is titled & ready for you to build your dream home. Perfect choice for both single and double storey homes.
The Grove Estate offers beautiful creek side living without sacrificing great access to education, retail amenities and recreational facilities.
